{"tid":50271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"力威師傅食藥先咁大隻","createTime":"2016-12-22T09:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T09:48:58.000Z","uid":5690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"434cacea9298c252d9441df8f305d0405d2149de","tid":50271,"uid":5690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T09:48:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老母個時Arnold選港男個個都話佢用藥我都唔信 <br />\n胡師傅又話乜師徒制唔會呃9人 又話唔贊成健美比賽 話9人用藥唔健康 又成日講力威健身 天然健身 我仲on99信佢<br />\n點撚知我琴日睇佢段新片 嘩屌Arnold細隻佐勁多 有乜可能由選港男到而家d肌肉會無哂<br />\n我就留言問點解Arnold會細隻佐咁多 佢佐極速del佐我留言 擺到明身有屎 咁你之前又話乜9自己天然健身 話乜9人用藥呀屌你 成撚日淨係識叫人掙扎<br />\n<br />\n片同對比圖係下面<br />\n舊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/99xpX47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F99xpX47.jpg&h=5aa04014&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/174555_f5e3c399e070280ae33d79384ce5fcd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F174555_f5e3c399e070280ae33d79384ce5fcd1.jpg&h=0508a2af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/22Nvs88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F22Nvs88.jpg&h=69598462&s={SIZE}\" />新<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/174557_246e9454ce02e171fac21e79c936f38f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F174557_246e9454ce02e171fac21e79c936f38f.jpg&h=c92be7d9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/174558_2e2a68e289027493da28fe8b8cc91c22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F174558_2e2a68e289027493da28fe8b8cc91c22.jpg&h=df5b1291&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片（7:14開始）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FrancosGymCollege/videos/625458304306930/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFrancosGymCollege%2Fvideos%2F62545830